  <title>Achieving layering</title>
  <para>
    It is often found that it is not easy to achieve a cleanly layered system. 
    believe that our use-case/responsibility driven approach can assist
    significantly in generating a cleanly layered architecture with
    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem><para>good responsibility localization and</para></listitem>
      <listitem><para>well defined layers of granularity.</para></listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
    <note><para>
      URDAD, the <emphasis>Use-Case/Responsibility Driven Analysis and Design</emphasis> process may
      make this task a lot easier.
    </para></note>
  </para>
  
